{"DamageImmunities":["Poison","Acid"],"ConditionImmunities":[],"DamageResistances":[],"DamageVulnerability":[],"SavingThrowBonuses":["Dex +9","Con +14","Int +12","Wis +9","Cha +4"],"SkillBonuses":["Skill: Perception (Wis) +18 | (Wis 2, Prof. 7, Bonus 9)"],"_Senses":["Blindsight 10 ft.","Darkvision 120 ft.","Passive Perception 21"],"_Languages":["Undercommon","Deep Speech","Draconic","Giant","Draconic","Common"],"_Abilities":[{"Title":"Amphibious","Description":"Mirikius can breathe air and water","isDamage":false,"isSpell":false,"attack":null,"saveDC":0},{"Title":"Legendary Resistance (3/day)","Description":"If Mirikius fails a saving throw, she can choose to succeed instead","isDamage":false,"isSpell":false,"attack":null,"saveDC":0},{"Title":"Antimagic Cone","Description":"Mirikius' central eye creates an area of antimagic, as in the antimagic field spell, in a 150 foot cone. At the start of each of her turns, Mirikius decides which way the cone faces and whether the cone is active. The Area works against Mirikius' own spells.","isDamage":false,"isSpell":false,"attack":null,"saveDC":0}],"_Actions":[{"Title":"Bite","Description":null,"isDamage":true,"isSpell":false,"attack":{"_Attack":"Melee Weapon Attack","Bonus":"15","Reach":5,"RangeClose":0,"RangeFar":0,"Target":"one target","HitDiceNumber":4,"HitDiceSize":6,"HitDamageBonus":0,"HitAverageDamage":14,"HitText":"and 9(2d8) acid damage","HitDamageType":"Piercing"},"saveDC":0},{"Title":"Acid Breath (Recharge 5-6)","Description":"Mirikius Exhales Acid in a 90ft line that is 10ft wide. Each Creature in that line must make a DC 22 dex saving throw, taking 15d8 acid damage on a failed save or half as much on a successful one","isDamage":false,"isSpell":false,"attack":null,"saveDC":0},{"Title":"Frightful Presence","Description":"Each Creature of Mirikius' Choice that is within 120 feet of her and aware of her must succeed on a dc19 Wisdom saving throw or become frightened for 1 minute, a creature can repeat the saving throw at the end of each of its turns, ending the effect on itself on a success. if a creature's saving throw is successful or the effect ends for it, the creature is immune to the Mirikius' Frightful Presence for the next 24 hours.","isDamage":false,"isSpell":false,"attack":null,"saveDC":0},{"Title":"Tail","Description":null,"isDamage":true,"isSpell":false,"attack":{"_Attack":"Melee Weapon Attack","Bonus":"15","Reach":20,"RangeClose":0,"RangeFar":0,"Target":"one target","HitDiceNumber":2,"HitDiceSize":8,"HitDamageBonus":8,"HitAverageDamage":17,"HitText":"","HitDamageType":"Bludgeoning"},"saveDC":0},{"Title":"Eye Rays","Description":" Mirikius has four eye rays that originate from her four smaller eyes, each eye has a range of 120 feet. She shoots two of these rays at random, choosing a creature she can see for each.\n 1. Death Ray\nIf the target is a creature it must succeed on a DC 20 Dexterity Saving throw or take 55(10d10) necrotic damage. The Target dies if the ray reduces it to 0 hit points\n 2. Telekinetic ray\nIf the target is a creature, it must succeed a DC 20 strength saving throw or Mirikius moves it up to 30ft in any direction. It is restrained by the ray's  telekinetic grip until the start of Mirikius' next turn or until Mirikius is Incapacitated.  If the target is an object weighing 300lb or less that isn't being worn or carried, it is moved up to 30ft away in any direction. Mirikius can exert fine control on objects with this ray, such as manipulating a simple tool or opening a door or a container.\n 3. Charm Ray\nThe Targeted creature must succeed a DC 20 wisdom saving throw or be charmed by Mirikius for 1 hour or until Mirikius harms the creature.\n 4. Paralyzing ray\nThe targeted creature must succeed on a DC 20 constitution saving throw or be paralyzed for 1 minute. The target can repeat the saving through at the end of each of its turns, ending the effect on itself on a success.","isDamage":false,"isSpell":false,"attack":null,"saveDC":0}],"_Reactions":[],"_Legendaries":[{"Traits":[{"Title":"Detect","Ability":"Mirikius makes a Wisdom (perception) check"},{"Title":"Eye Ray","Ability":"Mirikius uses one random Eye ray"},{"Title":"Wing Attack (costs 2 actions)","Ability":"Mirkius Beats her wings. Each creature within 15 feet must succeed on a  DC 23 Dexterity Saving Throw or take 15 (2d6+8) bludgeoning damage and be knocked prone. Mirikius can then fly up to half her speed"},{"Title":"Tail Attack","Ability":"Mirikius makes a Tail Attack"}],"Title":"Legedary Actions"}],"_advancedSpells":[],"_advancedSpellData":[],"Title":"","STR":27,"DEX":14,"CON":25,"INT":20,"WIS":15,"CHA":19,"proficency":7,"Speed":"50 ft., fly: 65 ft.","AC":"18 (Natural Armor)","HP":"367 (21d20 + 147)","CR":{"Index":26,"CR":"23","profBonus":7,"ArmorClass":19,"AttackBonus":11,"SaveDC":20,"LowHP":491,"HighHP":535,"XP":50000},"CreatureName":"Mirikius The Praised","CreatureSize":"Huge","CreatureType":"Aberration","CreatureAlign":"Neutral Evil","unique":false,"CreatureGender":"Female","LegendaryActions":"3"}